The paper discusses designing routing schemes in computer networks, which falls under the category of computer networks and communications (cs.NI). The paper also discusses fault-tolerance and resilience, which could fall under the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), social and information networks (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
